    dcterms:type <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/EventType/ConfigurationChange> .

<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/EventType/ConfigurationChange> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Configuration Change Event Type"@en .

noria:EventRecord_DBServer01_DiskCleaned
    dcterms:title "Database Disk Cleanup Completed" ;
